OL,5,Cprisoners
OL,7,FFamilies will deliver a petition to 10
OL,8,FDowning Street today (11 September)
OL,9,Fcalling on the UK Government to
OL,10,Fresentence IPP prisoners.
OL,12,FWhat is an IPP sentence?
OL,14,FImprisonment for Public Protection
OL,15,F(IPP) sentences were introduced in
OL,16,F2005 before being scrapped in 2012.
