OL,7,FHowever, the orders were not revoked
OL,8,Fretrospectively, meaning that two
OL,9,Fdecades since being brought in,
OL,10,Fthousands of people across the UK are
OL,11,Fstill subject to their conditions.
OL,13,FThe sentences were initially intended
OL,14,Fto be handed to the most serious
OL,15,Foffenders whose crimes did not warrant
OL,16,Fa life sentence, with the view that
OL,17,Fthey would only be released once re-
OL,18,Fhabilitated.
