OL,7,FShirley Debono from Cardiff is one of
OL,8,Fthose leading the campaign.
OL,10,FHer son, Shaun Lloyd, was originally
OL,11,Fsentenced to two and a half years in
OL,12,Fprison in 2005 after stealing a mobile
OL,13,Fphone, but spent nine consecutive
OL,14,Fyears behind bars. He is now currently
OL,15,Fback in prison after being recalled on
OL,16,Fhis IPP in March 2024.
