OL,7,FShe says behaviour linked to his drug
OL,8,Faddiction - which he developed in
OL,9,Fprison - has seen him recalled four
OL,10,Ftimes. According to Shirley, he has
OL,11,Fnow spent more than 12 years behind
OL,12,Fbars.
OL,14,FShe is now campaigning for all
OL,15,Fprisoners still serving an IPP to be
OL,16,Fre-sentenced.
