OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, she said:
OL,8,F"Shaun is feeling like he's in
OL,9,Farbitrary detention. It feels like
OL,10,Fit's torture- he's banged up 23 hours
OL,11,Fa day. Lately he's been doing this
OL,12,Fcourse, which has been good. He's
OL,13,Fgetting out, he's doing well on the
OL,14,Fprogramme and being praised for
OL,15,Fhelping other prisoners. But, he's
OL,16,Fstill going back to that cell.
