OL,7,F"If he was any other normal person he
OL,8,Fwouldn't be in prison. He was directed
OL,9,Ffor immediate release by the police,
OL,10,Fbut because he's an IPP prisoner he
OL,11,Fhas to stay inside. He has already
OL,12,Fbeen inside for 18 to 19 months now,
OL,13,Fand he's still not going to get out
OL,14,Ftill next year. That's a long time to
OL,15,Fbe in prison for something you haven't
OL,16,Fdone.
