OL,7,FThe petition states that a complaint
OL,8,Fhas been submitted to the United
OL,9,FNations' Working Group on Arbitrary
OL,10,FDetention, and aims to highlight that
OL,11,Fthe abolished Imprisonment for Public
OL,12,FProtection (IPP) sentence in the UK
OL,13,Fcontinues to result in the arbitrary
OL,14,Fdetention of prisoners.
OL,16,FIt will also request a response and
OL,17,Fformally invite the Prime Minister to
OL,18,Fa meeting on the topic.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/10
