OL,7,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "It is right that IPP sentences
OL,9,Fwere abolished. We are determined to
OL,10,Fmake progress towards safe and
OL,11,Fsustainable releases for those in
OL,12,Fprison, but not in a way that
OL,13,Fundermines public protection."
